<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_74" id="36v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_74_r2l23"><expan>VVeiſſemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_74_r2l24"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> / Als Seicʒ Noll <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> mitburger vnd Ratgeſelle nehſt von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vvegen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l25">an vns braht / von ſölcher klag wegen / als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> Burkhart Sebach <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l26">gen des Steffan Camrers ewrs <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> ſelıgen 
<del rend="strikethrough"> wegen </del> <expan>vormund<ex>en</ex></expan> auf dem </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l27">lantgerihte hie <expan>angefange<ex>n</ex></expan> het / Vnd wir den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> durch ewren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l28">willen daran weiſten / daʒ Er von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> klag laſſen vnd das recht vor ew </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l29">von <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ~ <expan>vormünde<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd nemen ſolt / hat vns der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l30"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> fürgelegt / vvie daʒ Er <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vveiſh<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>cʒekume<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l31">brief die Er hie <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex></expan> des gerihts <expan>Jnſ<ex>igel</ex></expan> hab fürcʒubringen vnd das reht von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l32">den ~ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> darauff vor euch cʒu <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">ne </del> cʒenemen maine / <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l33"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleiſſ<ex>iklichen</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr Jm <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günſtige hilff vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l34"><expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darẏnne bevveẏſen vvöllet / Alſo vvarcʒu Er reht hab / daʒ Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_74_r2l35">das on hindernüſſe vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>cʒieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> volg vnd werd Als etc das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_74" id="36v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Weissemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als Seicz Noll, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        mitburger und ratgeselle, nehst von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> wegen an
                        uns braht von sölcher klag wegen, als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> Burkhart
                        Sebach, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, gen des Steffan Camrers, ewrs
                                <expan>mitburg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> seligen,
                                <expan>vormund<ex>en</ex></expan> auf dem lantgerihte hie
                                <expan>angefange<ex>n</ex></expan> het, und wir den
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> durch ewren willen daran weisten, daz er von
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> klag lassen und das recht vor ew
                        von <expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vormünde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und nemen solt, hat uns der
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> fürgelegt, wie daz er
                                <expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>czekume<ex>n</ex></expan> und sein brief, die er hie
                                <expan>unt<ex>er</ex></expan> des gerihts
                            <expan>ins<ex>igel</ex></expan> hab, fürczubringen und das reht von den
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> darauff vor euch czu
                                <expan>vord<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und czenemen maine.
                                <expan>Bite<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleiss<ex>iklichen</ex></expan>, daz ir im
                            <expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff und
                            <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darynne beweysen wöllet. Also warczu er
                        reht hab, daz im das on hindernüsse und
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>czieh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> volg und werd, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
